The,Sinch,Verification,API,allows,developers,to,integrate,Sinch,phone,number,verification,services,into,their,applications,Developers,also,have,the,option,to,check,the,progress,of,an,ongoing,verification,request,in,order,to,understand,the,status,of,the,API,call,The,Sinch,Verification,API,supports,Flash,Call,Android,only,and,SMS,PIN,verification,for,iOS,Android,and,JavaScript